Package co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model

Class Order

java.lang.Object
co.edu.unbosque.electroshop_api.model.Order
@Entity public class Order extends Object
Entity representing an order placed by a customer.

This class defines the structure of an order within the system, including details such as the order date, payment method, status, total price, and associated customer and products.

    • Order

      public Order(Integer orderId, Date date, String paymentMethod, String status, Float totalPrice, Float priceWithIVA, Customer customer, List<OrderProduct> orderProducts)
      Constructs a new Order with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      orderId - the unique identifier for the order
      date - the date when the order was placed
      paymentMethod - the method used to pay for the order
      status - the current status of the order
      totalPrice - the total price of the order
      priceWithIVA - the total price of the order including IVA
      customer - the customer who placed the order
      orderProducts - the list of products included in the order
